On this branch saved working configs for configure
	 nginx+PHP-FPM (php7.3 and php 5.6)+SSL/TLS for Centos8/Centos7.
Configs are only for particular configuring  nginx+PHP-FPM services. 

:)

P.S.
On client needs to edit files /etc/resolv.conf and /etc/hosts

/etc/resolv.conf -----------> needs to add DNS server IPs
/etc/hosts -----------> needs to add IP<tab>FQDN_hosts
    EXAMPLE:
    xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx<TAB>test1.mainfqdn.local
    xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx<TAB>test2.mainfqdn.local
    xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx<TAB>test3.mainfqdn.local
    xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx<TAB>test4.mainfqdn.local

And, of course, run the command: 'systemctl restart NetworkManager'.
